PHP Local Variable Application: 

<html>
<head>
<title>Local Variable Application</title>
</head>
<body>
<?php
function varLocal() {
 $m = 5;
 $n = 12;
 $n = $m + $n;
 echo $n;
}
varLocal();
?>
</body>
</html>

PHP Global Variable Application:

<html>
<head>
<title>Global Variable Application</title>
</head>
<body>
<?php
$m = 6.5;
$n = 9;
function varGlobal() {
 GLOBAL $m, $n;
 $n = $m + $n;
}
varGlobal();
echo $n;
?>
</body>
</html>
